News.Title: Rajputana Biodiesel Wins ₹43.50 Crore Supply Contract and Gets Expansion Approval
News.Summary: Rajputana Biodiesel secured a tender to supply 5,405 KL of biodiesel worth ₹43.50 crore to three major oil companies: IOCL, BPCL, and HPCL. The company also received approval to expand its Phulera facility capacity to 90 KL per day. The company has a market capitalization of ₹190 crore.

News.Title: Rajputana Biodiesel: Stellar Stock Market Debut with 90% Premium
News.Summary: Rajputana Biodiesel shares listed on the stock market with a 90% premium over the issue price. The stock immediately hit the upper circuit limit after its debut.
